data.description: If you think rates are bad, you’ll hate living with the regret of missing out on this home! This home is an absolute charmer. From the corner lot to side load garage to the split floor plan - it offers SO much! Plus it’s in a great location. The Osage Praire Trail is just a hop, skip, and a jump away. From there you can head right into Skiatook and enjoy time at Skiatook Central Park. Back on the market at no fault of the seller! Move in ready, act fast!
